| Role Name            | Description                                                                                     |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Admin**            | Full access to the system. Manages users, roles, and system settings.                           |
| **Executive**        | High-level access to key solar performance metrics and dashboards.                              |
| **Engineer**         | Technical staff who monitor and troubleshoot plant performance.                                 |
| **Analyst**          | Data professionals who analyze trends, usage, and performance data.                             |
| **Field Technician** | On-site workers who may need read-only access to specific plant data.                           |
| **Client**           | External stakeholders or customers with limited, view-only access to relevant solar plant data. |


